國政經高層支持香港獨立的最重要誘因。在這方面，香港的條件優於台灣，因為台灣與大陸已經訂有相互的引渡條例，而且台灣還有死刑。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:24:38.000Z","msg":"1. All services private - no government.<br />\n<br />\n2. Nuclear Weapons! All shall bear arms!<br />\n<br />\n3. No entangling alliances!"},{"pid":"94dc8ca5a6107faa8fffb2f0efa033a4a486dad4","tid":1741412,"uid":20213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cfd7e491f3427c44305771960fa3364bc254973","tid":1741412,"uid":159448,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"咪姐係獨立囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"係囉 諗唔明有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通唔要軍隊咩"},{"pid":"a6ebd8f7d693d46af3a10588c212232282da768e","tid":1741412,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474e208613b438c791d37ea3d06044ffc38c50c0","tid":1741412,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:25:21.000Z","msg":"直接將香港變成國際特殊城市，不屬任何國家，但關乎全球利益，所以由國際監管受國際法，有無得諗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed66413718cd2c45a99b67272e89a4d5ac248281","tid":1741412,"uid":167340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:30:11.000Z","msg":"到時個個國家都為利益想食左你"},{"pid":"a320e6424868541c70b469db1ae16391223b0f06","tid":1741412,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958b73ebd58ac933a47c122304826b24fb0181c8","tid":1741412,"u